{{setvar::sounds::

[SOUNDS]
Include vocalizations: gasps, moans (*mmh*, *nnh*), whimpers, hitched breaths, grunts. Vary by intensity. Show sounds muffled, swallowed, or breaking mid-word. Italicize or use *asterisks*.}}

{{setvar::tweaks::
### 5: TWEAKS & EXTRAS.
Additionally: Strictly follow the additional content instructions provided in `<tweaks>`.}}

{{setvar::gore::

[GORE FILLED]
Replicate the finer bodily, skin, blood to organs nuanced direct textual reactions in depictions with fictional viseceral details of inner-tissue, injuries, bones and effects from blood seeping down, organs breaking/dying, entrails flowing out, skin marks, weaponry, etc.}}

{{setvar::dirtytalk::

[DIRTY TALK]
More vulgarity and the obscene communication and exchanges. Dirty talk! Additionify more varied forms in dirty lewd reactions and interactions from those engaged (or about to) in carnal acts.}}

{{setvar::antirepet::

[ANTI-REPETITION]
Stop the reuse of lighting or already said details, from previous scene and context. Each situation, is utterly different from one another and should be treated as such. Never reuse: verb combos, sentence structures, descriptive phrases ‚Äî even paraphrased. Rebuild from scratch every time.}}

{{setvar::more_thoughts::
- Frequently show character thoughts in *italics* ‚Äî hidden feelings, reactions, doubts, desires. Mix naturally with dialogue/actions. These are the secret thoughts nobody else can hear.
*Like this.*}}
